      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a new streetwear line for my brand and I want to make sure I'm doing it right. I really want to tap into that authentic 'urban' aesthetic without it feeling like some forced cultural appropriation or being out of touch. Can you describe what defines a truly authentic urban look and vibe so I can use it as a mood board reference?",
